# 🧠 Quick Troubleshooting Checklist

| Problem             | Solution               |
| ------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Apache not starting | Check port 80 conflict |
| MySQL not starting  | Check port 3306        |
| phpMyAdmin error    | Check config.inc.php   |
| Access denied       | Reset root password    |
| Blank localhost     | Check Apache logs      |

Logs location:

* Windows: `C:\xampp\apache\logs`
* Linux: `/opt/lampp/logs`

